1. *Albert* je bio veoma uspešan naučnik. (Albert was a very successful scientist.)
2. Studiram na *Albertovom* fakultetu. (I study at Albert's faculty.)
3. *Alberta* već neko vreme nismo videli. (We haven't seen Alberta for some time now.)
4. *Albertu* je odobren projekat. (Albert's project has been approved.)
5. *Alberte*, kako ti ide? (Albert, how are you doing?)
6. *Albertom* se ponose svi koji su ga poznavali. (Everyone who knew Albert is proud of him.)
7. *Albertove* knjige su veoma popularne. (Albert's books are very popular.)
8. *Alberti* su bili veoma ljubazni prema nama. (The Alberts were very kind to us.)
9. *Albertima* se divimo zbog njihovog uspeha. (We admire the Alberts for their success.)
10. U gradu postoji *Albertova* ulica. (There is a street called Albert's in the city.)